Subject: Arguments to 4.3BSD "sh -c" commands are mishandled
Index: bin/sh 4.3BSD

Description:
	Arguments to a "sh -c" command are mishandled.

Repeat-By:
	Type in the command
		sh -c 'echo $*' a b c d
	and note the incorrect output:
		b c d
